OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my workplace is
OL,4,Ctoo hot?
OL,6,FA red heat health alert has been
OL,7,Fissued for six regions of England
OL,8,Fduring the forecast heatwave on
OL,9,FWednesday and Thursday, indicating "a
OL,10,Frisk to life for even the healthy
OL,11,Fpopulation", the UK Health Security
OL,12,FAgency said.
OL,14,FThe Met Office said this week's
OL,15,Fheatwave will see temperatures exceed
OL,16,F37C in the shade and could even see
OL,17,Fthem rise to 38C to 40C in some parts
OL,18,Fof England and Wales.
