OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my workplace is
OL,4,Ctoo hot?
OL,6,FThe heatwave will have widespread
OL,7,Fimpacts on health and bring
OL,8,F"significant disruption" to daily
OL,9,Flife, leaving workers, from builders
OL,10,Fto office staff, sweltering outside or
OL,11,Finside with little or no access to air
OL,12,Fconditioning.
OL,14,FSo what are your rights if it's too
OL,15,Fhot to work? ITV News explains.
OL,17,FWhat if it's too hot to work?
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@XO]
