OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my workplace is
OL,4,Ctoo hot?
OL,6,FThere is no legal maximum working
OL,7,Ftemperature in the UK, meaning
OL,8,Femployees do not have an automatic
OL,9,Fright to stop working because it is
OL,10,Ftoo hot.
OL,12,FHowever, workers can still raise
OL,13,Fconcerns with their employer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
