OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my workplace is
OL,4,Ctoo hot?
OL,6,FWorking outdoors in hot weather can
OL,7,Fincrease the risk of heat stress,
OL,8,Fsunburn and long-term skin damage,
OL,9,Fincluding skin cancer.
OL,11,FThe HSE advises employers to:
OL,13,FThese are recommendations rather than
OL,14,Flegal requirements.
